<#include "base.ftl">
<#macro title>About</#macro>
<#macro content>
    <title>About</title>

    <div id="about" class="parallax-window relative" data-parallax="scroll" data-image-src="assets/img/antique-cafe-bg-03.jpg">
        <div class="container mx-auto tm-container pt-24 pb-48 sm:py-48">
            <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 p-12 pb-14 rounded-xl mb-5">
                <h2 class="mb-6 tm-text-green text-4xl font-medium">About our cafe</h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    Welcome to Antique Cafe, where delightful flavors and cozy ambiance come together to create an exceptional dining experience. Situated in the heart of Kazan, our café is the perfect destination for indulging in a culinary journey.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    At Antique Cafe, every dish is crafted with passion and precision, using only the finest locally sourced ingredients. Our menu offers a tantalizing selection of gourmet coffees, artisanal teas, and mouthwatering pastries that are sure to please even the most discerning palate. Whether you're craving a morning cappuccino, a light lunch, or a scrumptious dessert, our menu has something to satisfy every craving.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    Step inside our café and be greeted by our warm and friendly staff, who are dedicated to providing exceptional service and ensuring your visit is nothing short of memorable. The cozy and inviting atmosphere, accentuated by soft lighting and tasteful decor, sets the perfect backdrop for catching up with friends, conducting business meetings, or simply enjoying a peaceful moment alone.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    We believe that a great café experience is about more than just food and drinks. That's why we also offer complimentary Wi-Fi, creating an ideal space for remote work or catching up on your favorite book. Our commitment to sustainability is reflected in our eco-friendly practices, from responsibly sourced ingredients to compostable packaging.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    Whether you're a coffee connoisseur, a food enthusiast, or simply seeking a tranquil escape from the bustling city, Antique Cafe invites you to savor the flavors, embrace the ambience, and create unforgettable memories. Visit us today and discover why we are the go-to destination for café lovers in Kazan.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-8">
                    We look forward to welcoming you to our café soon!
                </p>
            </div>
            <a href="login" class="inline-block tm-bg-green transition text-white text-xl pt-3 pb-4 px-8 rounded-md">
                <i class="far fa-comments mr-4"></i>
                Login
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</#macro>
